{"tid":2159680,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"學者：警方不要繼續戀殖 派員到英國可能反被滲透","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T16:10:38.000Z","uid":5195,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8bad5df6fd2163b2f9e7967bc61bb9e4eb6a1fcb","tid":2159680,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"英國國防部因應與中國關係惡化等原因，暫停為香港警隊提供訓練課程。有學者指，既然英國「咁決絕」，香港警方以至所有紀律部隊亦應看清形勢，<span class=\"red\">不要繼續戀殖</span>，應停止派員到英國以至五眼聯盟等國家受訓；步操亦應用放棄英式，而是改用中式步操，否則本港回歸23年，加上《港區國安法》已訂立，若仍繼續使用英式步操及以風笛手伴奏，只會貽笑大方，認為今年十.一步操應與英國殖民地時代正式說再見。<br />\n<br />\n理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強表示，對於英國國防部表示暫停為香港警隊提供演練指導課程，其中一個原因是與中國關係惡化，「既然都講到咁決絕，香港警隊以致所有紀律部隊都應摒棄英國是前宗主國心態，全面停止派員到英國等五眼聯盟國家受訓，改為返回內地接受訓練。」<br />\n<br />\n陳又謂，自去年反修例示威，英美已表示停止向本港供應武器，本港紀律部隊便應思考自身定位，究竟是三不象還是認清方向，特別是中方正與五眼聯盟博弈，派員到英國受訓，<span class=\"red\">可能反被滲透</span>，故本港應就國家安全問題，暫停派員到海外受訓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f640d27824b778167b8856f5b3e2cef4d9b0c74","tid":2159680,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"跌落地下 那返渣沙"},{"pid":"6e70a5396977e30cb27e1fbdb066cb28637160d3","tid":2159680,"uid":82935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"正名 支那公安"},{"pid":"ed1a45b2481dfa5a0695b896ceb3658568d7ad16","tid":2159680,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecee2c11dfdd55207b9e596502774a15f78f2005","tid":2159680,"uid":103981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"不要戀殖 廢止長俸"},{"pid":"104f9b8540e0028bd2fec051937fe48d68c6241b","tid":2159680,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=0d2f1efa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"d282f36177243640458ff2456bcc1ed9ec4856c3","tid":2159680,"uid":13308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n返大陸受訓啦<br />\n又平d又有海底撈食"},{"pid":"69b9d587ec8309a5731aecc9ce621bc04297d8e6","tid":2159680,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"又係陳偉強條傻西<br />\n頭上面得幾條毛,廣東話都未講得正<br />\n學歷又廢<br />\n學人叫自己學者"},{"pid":"358242c746c63270dbeaa32b940af96b6a71d37a","tid":2159680,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"曲到圓"},{"pid":"0206edab860fd811b104d17916f9793ff1aecac6","tid":2159680,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"改名做公安部"},{"pid":"3dd7a8d9a1db6eb228dbdfb150a8fc2d62842989","tid":2159680,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"睇第一段已經知又係陳生嘅傑作"}]}